data.description: This Cape Cod in Wilmore/ Twyckenham Hills says "Welcome Home!" just in time for the holidays! A charming home showcasing professional craftsmanship and is impeccably maintained. It offers a perfect blend of classic elegance and modern comfort with its color scheme, cabinetry, and updated light fixtures. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath has natural lighting all throughout the home and a cozy fireplace with an electric fireplace insert in the main level bedroom. Please note that while there is an electric fireplace insert in the gas fireplace, the gas fireplace is not currently operational. Newer water heater (2015) and furnace (2013). The property includes a detached 2-car garage as well as a back yard with 2 levels for entertaining guests. This home has been loved and is ready to make new memories!
